title: Campus Police Dept - Season 4
description:
Campus Police Dept - Season 4

Campus PD is produced by Cineflix Productions. The show is similar in style and tone to the show COPS.

Unlike COPS, Campus PD focuses specifically on college and university campuses and towns and the authorities who patrol them
